data.name: description2.Text
data.value: For your bestie - an adorable memento of your friendship, made to keep forever. Add on your favourite photo together to add that extra special touch - and voila! You're done. This mug makes for a great gift for bridesmaids, birthdays, or simply just because.

data.name: description4.Text
data.value:
Wish the birthday girl a fabulous celebration, with our fabulous pink birthday mug! Add on your favourite photo together, along with her name or your chosen text - for that extra personal touch.
A customized mug is sure to be a statement piece on your shelf. Printed with heat transfer printing. The color is coated in outer appearance only.
